metadata.name: Seker Factory DAO Mintathon 002
metadata.description: Commemorates the second Seker Factory DAO live stream on koop.xyz, brought to you in collaboration with decent.xyz and koop.xyz. This mint helped continue the stream. 5% of the proceeds will go to a randomly selected collector at the conclusion of the stream. 20% will go towards a charity voted on by the community and the remaining proceeds will go to the Seker DAO Treasury to support upcoming projects focused on public goods and decentralized curation.
